
initramfs-tools uses bzr for it's devlopment:

# Debian repository
bzr branch http://arch.debian.org/arch/kernel/trunk/initramfs-tools/

# old jbailey repo
bzr branch http://people.ubuntu.com/~jbailey/bzrtree/initramfs-tools           
                                                                               
# Update your branch                                                           
bzr pull                                                                       
